# SilverTrack – Environment Configuration

Copy this file to `.env` and fill in values for your local setup.

# ── Database mode ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Set DB_TYPE to "mysql" to use a local MySQL server.
# Leave it as "sqlite" (or unset) to use the default SQLite file.
DB_TYPE=sqlite

# ── MySQL settings (only needed when DB_TYPE=mysql) ──────────────────────────
MYSQL_HOST=localhost
MYSQL_PORT=3306
MYSQL_USER=silvertrack
MYSQL_PASSWORD=change_me
MYSQL_DATABASE=silvertrack

# ── Flask settings ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Set to "1" to enable the interactive Flask debugger (development only).
FLASK_DEBUG=0
